reviews.comment: This seller is wonderful. I briefly described my request and she designed a logo in less than ten minutes. She also did a beautiful, professional social media kit that we really like. Great experience.

Fantastic work and quick turnaround. Easy to explain tiny tweaks that were completed in minutes. I am very impressed, I should add that my project was submitted on New Year's Eve and completed on New Year's Day, so extra thanks are required from me for that undertaking. I would highly recommend maleehagfx and will no doubt be in touch in the future for any other graphics work. Thank you so much. An absolute gem.

I have been working with her for over a year now to create artwork for new episodes. She is always responsive, on time, and willing to make the required changes with quick turnaround.  In addition, she is very kind and it's great to work with her. The initial design was spot on to convey the brand and intent of the podcast.

The artist was very talented and really took the time to understand what I was looking for. I really appreciate the multiple iterations and the quality of the output! Thank you for your great work, would definitely recommend to other!

Thank you for the wonderful work. You were great to work with and i love how you brought the vision to life! I will definitely keep you in mind for future work. Thank again! Highly recommended, The Awesome Lawsons approve!
